      <div id="page_head" style="margin-bottom:0px; padding-bottom:5px;"><span style="width: 100%;"><a id="skip_menu"></a></span>
       <h1>Henry A. Kissinger Program in Foreign Policy and International Relations </h1></div>
     <div class="box_img w_cap" style="margin-top:10px; padding-top:0px;"><a href="http://www.loc.gov/pictures/item/2003688492/"><img src="images/kissinger-chair-banner.jpg" width="694" height="150" alt="[Henry Kissinger with Egyptian President Sadat]. 1975." /></a></div>
<p class="header_cap"><a href="http://www.loc.gov/pictures/item/2003688492/">Henry Kissinger with Egyptian President Sadat.  1975.</a></p>   
<ul class="tabnav">
  <li class="first"><a href="#tab1">About</a></li>
  <li><a href="#tab2">Scholars </a></li>
