<h2>By Nomination Only</h2>
<p>There will be no direct applications for the  Kissinger Lecturer but nominations are welcome                  and may be submitted at any time to:</p>
<p> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Kissinger Chair Steering Committee<br />
  &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;c/o Office of Scholarly Programs<br />
  &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Library of Congress<br />
  &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;101 Independence Avenue S.E.<br />
  &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Washington, D.C. 20540-4860</p>
<p>Or, nominations may be submitted by fax or email:</p>
<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;202-707-3595 (fax)<br>
  &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;scholarly@loc.gov (email) </p>
<p>Telephone nominations will not be                  accepted.</p>
